BT /F2 22 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 740 Tm (AspieDad Communication Guide) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 720 Tm (A one-page summary with practical communication help for both NT and Aspie readers.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 684 Tm (3 Helpful Tactics For NT Readers) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 662 Tm (1. Be direct and specific.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 102 646 Tm (Say the real need clearly instead of hinting or expecting it to be inferred.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 624 Tm (2. Acknowledge before solving.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 102 608 Tm (If the moment is emotional, let the Aspie person know what matters first, then move to fixes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 586 Tm (3. Use one issue at a time.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 102 570 Tm (Keeping the conversation narrow reduces overload and improves the chance of being understood.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 532 Tm (3 Helpful Tactics For Aspie Readers) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 510 Tm (1. Say the care out loud.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 102 494 Tm (Do not assume your love or concern is obvious. NT spouses often need it spoken clearly.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 472 Tm (2. Acknowledge feelings before facts.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 102 456 Tm (Start with: "I can see this hurt you" before moving into logic, analysis, or correction.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 434 Tm (3. Return after processing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 102 418 Tm (If you need time, say so directly and come back. Silence without return can feel like rejection.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 382 Tm (3 Simple Phrases For NT Readers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 362 Tm (1. "Can you tell me what you heard me say?") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 346 Tm (2. "I am not hinting. What I need is...") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 330 Tm (3. "We can stay with one issue at a time.") Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 294 Tm (3 Simple Phrases For Aspie Readers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 274 Tm (1. "I care about you, even if I am struggling to show it.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 258 Tm (2. "I need a few minutes to process, but I will come back.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 242 Tm (3. "Do you want comfort, help, or for me just to listen?") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 90 Tm (AspieDad.com | Building understanding between NT and Aspie family life) Tj ET
